#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​But others are "
"looking for guidance. In that case, they book a meeting"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>Otras personas solo "
"buscan recibir orientación. En ese caso, programan una reunión"

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​From there, an "
"Opportunity is created in the the CRM and a salesperson is assigned to that "
"request.<br/>\n"
"                    <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​"
"After some preliminary discussions, the lead will move to the Territory "
"Research stage, where the salesperson <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: "
"1.28333px;\"> </span>​will perform some\n"
"                    analysis to see which of the available billboard_rental "
"is best for their campaign"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>Desde allí se crea "
"una oportunidad en CRM y se asigna un vendedor a esa solicitud.<br/>\n"
"                    <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​"
"Luego de algunas conversaciones, el lead pasa a la fase de estudio de área, "
"en la que el vendedor <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 1.28333px;\"> </"
"span>​realizará algunos\n"
"                    análisis para ver cuál de los paneles publicitarios "
"disponibles es el mejor para la campaña"

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​Further down the "
"process a Quotation is created. This is where the available Billboard will "
"be selected.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​La siguiente parte "
"del proceso es crear un presupuesto en donde deberá seleccionar el panel "
"disponible.<br/>"

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​It is also at this "
"point that one needs to decide which kind of subscription to use (short or "
"long term)."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​En este momento "
"también deberá decidir qué tipo de suscripción utilizará (a corto o largo "
"plazo)."

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​The company handles "
"two kinds of leads.<br/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​"
"First, they get requests from customers that want a specific "
"billboard_rental, for example because they saw it in the <span class=\"oe-"
"tabs\" style=\"width: 15.3px;\"> </span>​streets. For those\n"
"                    a lead is created manually, directly in the CRM, while "
"the prospect is on the phone."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​La compañía trabaja "
"con dos tipos de leads.<br/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </"
"span>Reciben solicitudes de clientes que quieren alquilar un panel "
"publicitario en específico, por ejemplo, porque la vieron en alguna <span "
"class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 15.3px;\"> </span>calle. Para ellos\n"
"                    se crea el lead manualmente en CRM durante la llamada."

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​To quickly encode the "
"orders, salespersons use Quotation Templates, that already contain the basic "
"packages."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"> </span>​Para realizar "
"rápidamente los pedidos, los vendedores utilizan plantillas de presupuestos "
"que incluyen los paquetes básicos."

#. module: billboard_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:billboard_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"><u> </u></span><u>​B) "
"Quotations</u>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"oe-tabs\" style=\"width: 40px;\"><u> </u></span><u>​B) "
"Presupuestos</u>"

